# Gradle wrapper IS committed (gradlew, gradlew.bat, gradle-wrapper.jar) so CI
# (GitHub Actions / Forgejo) can run ./gradlew directly against the sha256-pinned
# Gradle 8.11.1 distribution without re-generating the wrapper. bootstrap.sh
# remains for fresh local clones but is a no-op when the wrapper is present.

